                          <header class="nbcnews-dc-header cf">
                            <h2 class="nbcnews-dc-heading"><a href="https://www.nbcnews.com/card/rami-malek-wins-best-actor-n975511">Rami Malek wins for best actor</a></h2>
                          </header>
                      <div itemprop="articleBody">
                                          <p> Rami Malek takes home the Oscar for best actor for his role in "Bohemian Rhapsody." This is Malek's first Oscar nomination and win. In a heartfelt speech, the actor encouraged his fans to continue to find their voice, truth and live unapologetticaly. "Listen, we made a film about a gay man, an immigrant. A man that was unapologetically himself." </p>
                                          <p> Paying homage to his character, singer and songwriter Freddie Mercury, Malek noted "I am the son of immigrants from Egypt. I am a first generation American. Part of my story is being written right now." Mercury was also an immigrant who was battling AIDS during the height of his career. </p>
                                              <section class="nbcnews-dc-section">
                                                  <figure class="nbcnews-dc-embed_graphic">
                                                      <noscript><img class="img-responsive img_inline" src="https://media4.s-nbcnews.com/j/newscms/2019_08/2763961/190224-rami-malek-oscars-award-ac-1057p_f8f7503f2dcd975d05f56f24298522d2.nbcnews-ux-600-700.jpg"
                                                                     alt="Image: Rami Malek, 91st Academy Awards - Oscars - Hollywood" title="" itemprop="image"/></noscript>
                                              
                                                      <a href="https://media4.s-nbcnews.com/j/newscms/2019_08/2763961/190224-rami-malek-oscars-award-ac-1057p_f8f7503f2dcd975d05f56f24298522d2.nbcnews-ux-2880-1000.jpg" class="js-lightbox lightbox_link">
                                                          <button class="btn btn_overlay"><i class="fa fa-expand"></i></button>
