                                                               data-original="https://media4.s-nbcnews.com/j/newscms/2019_08/2763961/190224-rami-malek-oscars-award-ac-1057p_f8f7503f2dcd975d05f56f24298522d2.nbcnews-ux-600-700.jpg" alt="Image: Rami Malek, 91st Academy Awards - Oscars - Hollywood" title=""/>
                                                      </a>
                                              
