                          <header class="nbcnews-dc-header cf">
                            <h2 class="nbcnews-dc-heading"><a href="https://www.nbcnews.com/card/oscar-quiz-hollywood-inclusion-riders-n975301">Oscars quiz: Inclusion rider mentions at the Academy Awards</a></h2>
                          </header>
                      <div itemprop="articleBody">
                                          <p> <em>We’re asking ten questions, you'll get the next one after you answer this one, and if you stay on this device we’ll keep track of your score.</em> </p>
                                          <p> <strong>Hollywood is kind of sort of coming to grips with its diversity problem. Don’t be surprised if you start hearing a lot more about “inclusion riders.”</strong> </p>
                                  <div class="nbcnews-dc-section">
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
