                            <h2 class="nbcnews-dc-heading"><a href="https://www.nbcnews.com/card/netflix-drops-teaser-trailer-its-scorsese-movie-n975461">Netflix drops a teaser trailer for its Scorsese movie</a></h2>
                          </header>
                      <div itemprop="articleBody">
                                          <p> Netflix has picked quite a moment to drop a teaser trailer for its upcoming movie, "The Irishman," directed by Martin Scorsese.  </p>
