                          <header class="nbcnews-dc-header cf">
                            <h2 class="nbcnews-dc-heading"><a href="https://www.nbcnews.com/card/oscars-2019-quiz-ellen-degeneres-selfie-n975241">Oscars quiz: Who *wasn&#x27;t* in the famous Ellen DeGeneres selfie?</a></h2>
                          </header>
                      <div itemprop="articleBody">
                                          <p> <em>We’re asking ten questions, you'll get the next one after you answer this one, and if you stay on this device we’ll keep track of your score.</em> </p>
                                          <p> <strong>The selfie. The defining art form of this modern era — and the centerpiece of one of the most authentically fun moments in recent Oscar history.</strong> </p>
                                  <div class="nbcnews-dc-section">
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
